          "title": "How to automate troubleshooting a k8s cluster environment",
          "abstract": "This session will introduce troubleshoot.sh, an open source project that helps diagnose common issues that could impact the successful deployment and operation of a Kubernetes cluster. We'll talk about how to use out-of-the-box tools, plus show you how to write your own custom collectors and analysers. Together these components should help identify issues before you install and once you are up and running.",
