      "name":"Anton Sankov","image":"https://sessionize.com/image/1422-400o400o2-Xnscsrh36NdKfqcuZX1S1f.jpeg","href": "https://twitter.com/a_sankov",
      "bio":"Anton is a software engineer at VMware Carbon Black. He has a strong engineering background, having previously worked at market leaders in multiple industries - from payments, to cloud and infrastructure provisioning. At VMware, he is helping define the future of container and cloud security. The Kubernetes ecosystem is interesting to him because of its elegant solutions to real-world problems and constant drive for innovation.",
